# Naval Support Activity Naples  

**Location in Italy**  

Naval Support Activity Naples (NSA Naples) is a United States Navy military complex, located adjacent to [Naples International Airport](/Naples_International_Airport) in [Capodichino](/Capodichino), Naples, Italy.^[1] The facility sits within the [Campania](/Campania) region of southern Italy and shares its perimeter with the historic volcanic landscape that frames the Bay of Naples.  

